Sentencas: The La06Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF48) film was deposited on Crofer 22 APU ferritic stainless steel using the pulsed laser deposition (PLD) technique.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The LSCF48 film with a thickness of about 1.1 mu m was dense and homogeneous, with good adhesion to the metallic substrate.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Transmission electron microscopy combined with the energy-dispersive X-ray spectroscopy studies showed that the stoichiometry of the target was precisely transferred to the film by pulsed laser deposition.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Oxidation studies of bare Crofer 22 APU steel, and steel with the LSCF48 film were carried out in laboratory air at 1073 K under both isothermal and cyclic oxidation conditions.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The calculated parabolic rate constant k(p) after oxidation for 200 h for the steel with LSCF48 film was approximately three times lower than the oxidation rate of the steel without surface modification.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The oxide scale formed on Crofer 22 APU steel consisted of two layers: an inner layer built of chromia and an outer layer consisting of the Mn1.5Cr1.5O4 spinel.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: In the case of the steel with LSCF48 film, the oxide scale was two times thinner and had a similar phase composition.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: In both cases, the presence of an internal oxidation zone with SiO2 and Al2O3 precipitates was observed.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: In addition, small amounts of spinel crystals were observed on the film surface.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: After 2400 h of oxidation at 1073 K under thermal cyclic conditions, the total mass gain was 1.04 mg .
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: cm(-2) for the respectively bare and coated substrate.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The results indicated that the spallation of the oxide scale and/or the film did not occur.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: In both cases, the composition of the scales was similar to the scales formed on the samples after isothermal oxidation.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Studies of the electrical properties show, that Crofer 22 APU steel with LSCF48 film deposited by PLD method meets criteria for the interconnector materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells applications.
Titulo: High-temperature oxidation behavior of the Crofer 22 APU steel coated with (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 film prepared by pulsed laser deposition
